'''冠军成长股份有限公司'''（{{Lang-en|Canopy Growth Corporation}}），其前身为“特威德大麻股份公司（{{lang|en|Tweed Marijuana Inc.}}）”，是一家位于[[加拿大|加拿大]][[安大略省|安大略省]][[拉纳克县|拉纳克县]]{{Link-en|史密斯瀑布镇|Smiths Falls}}的一家{{Link-en|大麻产业|Cannabis industry}}公司。公司于2009年8月5日建立，创始人为布鲁斯·林顿（{{lang|en|Bruce Linton}}）<ref name="CNN_Profile" />；在与加拿大倍德罗坎（{{lang|en|Bedrocan Canada}}）合并后，公司于2015年改用现名。

截至2019年4月，根据冠军成长公司的股票市值及资产价值，其业已成为全球最大的大麻公司<ref>{{cite web |author1=Scott Deveau |author2=Kristine Owram |author3=Craig Giammona |title=Canopy Growth Is Near a Deal to Acquire Acreage Holdings |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-04-17/canopy-growth-is-said-to-near-deal-to-acquire-acreage-holdings |publisher=[[彭博社|彭博社]] |accessdate=2020-08-08 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128154943/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-04-17/canopy-growth-is-said-to-near-deal-to-acquire-acreage-holdings |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在当时，{{Link-en|星座品牌|Constellation Brands}}占有该公司35%的股份<ref>{{cite web |author1=Craig Giammona |author2=Brandon Kochkodin |title=Marijuana Bet Paying Off for Alcohol Giant Constellation Brands |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-04-18/marijuana-bet-paying-off-for-alcohol-giant-constellation-brands |publisher=[[彭博社|彭博社]] |accessdate=2020-08-08 |archive-date=2019-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716142158/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-04-18/marijuana-bet-paying-off-for-alcohol-giant-constellation-brands |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但是公司在2019年遭遇了极大的挑战，公司的股票价格下跌了约32%<ref>{{cite web |author1=Nicole Gibillini |title=Canopy names Constellation’s David Klein as its new CEO |url=https://www.bnnbloomberg.ca/canopy-growth-names-constellation-s-david-klein-as-its-new-ceo-1.1359697 |publisher=[[彭博社|彭博社]] |accessdate=2020-08-08 |archive-date=2020-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922134453/https://www.bnnbloomberg.ca/canopy-growth-names-constellation-s-david-klein-as-its-new-ceo-1.1359697 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

